Package: snes9x-gtk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: portable Super Nintendo Entertainment System emulator
 Snes9x is a Super Nintendo Entertainment System (SNES) emulator written in
 C++. This package provides the GTK3 graphical frontend.
 .
 It emulates the SNES CPU, PPU (graphics), APU (audio), and co-processors
 including the Super FX, SA-1, DSP-1/2/3/4, S-DD1, and others. Netplay,
 save states, game genie/pro action replay codes, and multiple sound drivers
 (ALSA, PulseAudio, PortAudio) are supported.
 .
 SNES ROMs are not included. Users must supply their own legally obtained
 game files.
